Ayah...

6
00:00:27,940 --> 00:00:29,990
Ini tidak benar. Ayah.

7
00:00:36,650 --> 00:00:38,770
Ayah!

8
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,350
Ayah...

9
00:00:41,350 --> 00:00:43,720
cepat bangun.

10
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:46,130
Ayo kita pulang.

11
