00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:37,920
Sudah berkali-kali kucari.

228
00:24:37,920 --> 00:24:41,260
Sepertinya mereka bunganya sudah dicabut.

229
00:24:43,950 --> 00:24:50,230
Aku ingin berikan bunga itu pada
Hye Ryeong kalau dia sudah pulang.

230
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:57,040
Dia pasti akan sangat menyukai bunga itu.

231
00:24:57,920 --> 00:25:01,720
Antar nyonya kedalam.

232
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:04,310
Baik, nona.

233
00:25:05,130 --> 00:25:07,800
